description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a Registered Nurse looking for an exciting opportunity within a Learning &amp; Development team? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here at Somerset NHS Foundation Trust we have just that on offer!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the OSCE team, you will be supporting aspiring Overseas Nurses across Somerset NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with other Clinical Skills Trainers, Practice Educators and the OSCE Lead you will be supporting and facilitating excellent learning opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Would you like to work in one of the most desirable places within the UK?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working in Somerset, you can soak up all that the idyllic countryside has to offer with our areas of outstanding beauty and stunning coastlines. You get to enjoy these perks whilst still only being a stone’s throw away from bustling city centres like Bristol, Bath and Exeter and only two hours away from London.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are excellent educational facilities in the area and, when compared to other regions, house prices are reasonable. You get to experience the best of both in Somerset, the countryside and the cosmopolitan – there is truly something for everyone!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Is this the ideal role for you? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are you looking to develop your career?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are you enthusiastic, motivated with a passion to support and inspire others?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do you already have experience in supporting learners in practice?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do you have the added advantage of experience of OSCE and/or Overseas Nursing?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you answered yes to these questions then we would love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further detailsplease contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sarah Harris, OSCE Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sarah.harris@somersetft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01823 342590&lt;/p&gt;
